Achievements.Name: Touge Fast, Touge Furious
Achievements.Description: You shutout an opponent in a career Touge event.

Achievements.Name: C-C-C-Combo Maker
Achievements.Description: You reached the maximum multiplier in an Overtake event.

Achievements.Name: All Night Long
Achievements.Description: You took part in and completed an online Endurance race.

Achievements.Name: Pinball Wizard
Achievements.Description: You traded paint with every competitor during one offline race and still won the race.

Achievements.Name: Mo Money, No Problems
Achievements.Description: You've gone above and beyond the call of duty and completed 5 career sponsor objectives.

Achievements.Name: Vanishing Point
Achievements.Description: You've won a race in a white Dodge Challenger but lived to tell the tale, unlike Kowalski.

Achievements.Name: Rocket Manski
Achievements.Description: You've driven faster than a Russian torpedo, which incidentally is 230 mph.

Achievements.Name: Sellout
Achievements.Description: You've got one thing on your mind: money! You completed 20 career sponsor objectives.

Achievements.Name: One For The Team
Achievements.Description: You've completed an individual Global Challenge goal and ultimately helped the community.

Achievements.Name: A Different Class
Achievements.Description: You've upgraded a car and bumped it to 'Upgraded' class.

Achievements.Name: Ring Master
Achievements.Description: You finished 5 seconds ahead of the target time in a Vehicle Challenge on the Red Bull Ring.

Achievements.Name: Tokyo Drift
Achievements.Description: You scored 350,000 drift points in Okutama in a Mazda RX-7 TYPE RZ or a NISMO R34T-R Z-TUNE.

Achievements.Name: Shaken, Not Stirred
Achievements.Description: You rolled a car at least 7 times and landed on its wheels, just like Bond did.

Achievements.Name: Keep Your Friends Close...
Achievements.Description: and your enemies even closer. You beat a Rival on track.

Achievements.Name: You rOCDed!
Achievements.Description: You finished first in every career event, during season play and/or via the timeline.

Achievements.Name: Dipping Your Toes
Achievements.Description: You've reached level 10 online and opened up a new world of possibilities.

Achievements.Name: Social Butterfly
Achievements.Description: You took part in an online playlist and stuck around for at least 5 races.

Achievements.Name: Sideways Shenanigans
Achievements.Description: You performed a 100m drift.

Achievements.Name: Could It Be Magic?
Achievements.Description: You beat all of the Prestige drivers in career club events.

Achievements.Name: Master Racer
Achievements.Description: You won a career event on the hardest difficulty without using Flashbacks.

Achievements.Name: Harder, Better, Faster, Stronger
Achievements.Description: You won a race in an upgraded car.

Achievements.Name: A Vision of What's to Come
Achievements.Description: You won a career Promo Event.

Achievements.Name: Beginner's Luck
Achievements.Description: You set the fastest time on the first lap of a Time Attack event.

Achievements.Name: Remember Me?
Achievements.Description: You lapped a competitor.

Achievements.Name: Eat It!
Achievements.Description: You won the first round of a career Touge event using the 5 second rule.

Achievements.Name: Making My Way Down Town
Achievements.Description: You've driven more than 1,000 miles (1,610km).

Achievements.Name: Pedal to the Medal
Achievements.Description: You won a round of a career event without using the brakes.

Achievements.Name: SWAGtastic!
Achievements.Description: You beat the target time in a Vehicle Challenge.

Achievements.Name: Global Domination
Achievements.Description: You won a week of Global Challenge.

Achievements.Name: California Dreaming
Achievements.Description: You completed California Big Sur in under 3 minutes.

Achievements.Name: Jack of All Trades
Achievements.Description: You've competed in all race types.

Achievements.Name: Natural Ability
Achievements.Description: You won an Online Playlist event.

Achievements.Name: The Artist
Achievements.Description: You've individually applied customised liveries to 5 vehicles.

Achievements.Name: Quantum Leap
Achievements.Description: You repeated an event using the Timeline.

Achievements.Name: Gone in 60 Seconds
Achievements.Description: You completed a lap of Chicago - Wabash Run driving the Ford Mustang Mach 1 in less than 60 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Harlem Globeshaker
Achievements.Description: You raced at every city at least once.

Achievements.Name: Drifting Like a Boss
Achievements.Description: You've scored 250,000 points in a single drift.

Achievements.Name: Flawless Victory
Achievements.Description: You've won an Overtake event making no contact with anything. (Excludes Global Challenge events)

Achievements.Name: Winging It
Achievements.Description: You've won a LiveRoute event.

Achievements.Name: Here's My Number, Call Me Maybe?
Achievements.Description: You returned Callahan's call and became his poster boy for the World Series of Racing.

Achievements.Name: That New Showroom Smell
Achievements.Description: Having wowed the crowds in America, it's time to upgrade your digs.

Achievements.Name: Oriental Express
Achievements.Description: Look out Asia, here we come.

Achievements.Name: Going Global
Achievements.Description: The WSR goes from regional to global thanks to your impressive form.

Achievements.Name: Even Balboa Had a Montage
Achievements.Description: The WSR is so big now that it's even getting montages on TV. You've made it to the big time!

Achievements.Name: The World's Greatest
Achievements.Description: Congratulations, you have become the ultimate WSR champion. What an investment!

Achievements.Name: T3XT M3SSAG1NG I5 GR8
Achievements.Description: Thanks to you, the WSR is now the talk of the town.

Achievements.Name: Internet Famous
Achievements.Description: The message boards are alight with the talk of the WSR's increasing popularity.

Achievements.Name: Clubbed to Death
Achievements.Description: That's it, folks. The club format is behind you, it's all about the leagues now. Good luck!

Achievements.Name: Toca Juniors No More
Achievements.Description: You got your first taste of a Super Touring Car and never looked back.

Achievements.Name: Imma Let You Finish
Achievements.Description: You amassed more fans than Taylor Swift has Twitter followers. That's 23.5 million, by the way.
